<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA94">
<l>viruppiṉā ṉīpiriya killāyō vēṟā</l>
<l>viruppiṭamaṟ ṟillaiyō veṉṉō - poruppaṉmakaṇ</l>
<l>mañcupōṉ mālviṭaiyāy niṟpirintu vēṟirukka</l>
<l>vañcumō collā yavaḷ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Are you not able to separate out of longing or else</l>
<l>are you without another residence? What? The mountain lord’s daughter,</l>
<l>you with a big bull like a [white] cloud, does she fear to become different (~ die),</l>
<l>separated from you, speak?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
